{"id":567210,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/09/【立此存照】观看爱国教育节目、提交观看照片成/","date":"2017-09-02T04:40:04Z","modified":"2017-10-16T17:44:42Z","title":"【立此存照】观看爱国教育节目、提交观看照片成中小学生开学作业","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>《开学第一课》节目由教育部和央视联合制作，每年开学当天播出。微博上有许多家长抱怨，称今年开学日，全国各地中小学校接教委通知，将观看该节目布置为作业、写观后感，甚至还有不少学校要求家长提供学生观看节目时与电视机的合照。另外，有网民称强行规定观看《开学第一课》的要求在某些地区已进行了多年。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/6169658559/FjUsuwh1R\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@宿州应用技术学校</a>：#开学第一课#【宿州应用技术学校积极组织师生收看开学第一课】9月1日，新学期开学第一天，宿州应用技术学校根据学校实际情况，通过校园办公平台向教师和学生发出收看央视《开学第一课》通知，要求全体师生准时收看，安排学生写观看心得并组织检查评比。@埇桥区教体局</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7mihibj31390qok0t.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567211\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7mihibj31390qok0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7mihibj31390qok0t.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7mihibj31390qok0t-300x204.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7j1n93j30m80cigmu.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567214\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7j1n93j30m80cigmu.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7j1n93j30m80cigmu.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7j1n93j30m80cigmu-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7l8s74j30zk0qomzo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7l8s74j30zk0qomzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7l8s74j30zk0qomzo.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7l8s74j30zk0qomzo-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7lra2vj30qo0zkadl.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7lra2vj30qo0zkadl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7lra2vj30qo0zkadl.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/006Jxg1Vly1fj4x7lra2vj30qo0zkadl-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a>​​​​</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1730252035/FjUwh95zY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@一四班家委会</a>：#安阳校园# 新学年，新气象，开学第一课精彩的节目引人入胜。安阳钢城小学二年级四班同学们在家认真观看央视一套 开学第一课节目。同学们纷纷表示祖国传统文化博大精深，作为祖国新一代要努力学习，做好中华文化继承人，把祖国传统文化发扬光大！@安阳市钢城小学 @安阳市教育局 ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xifhh8yj20zk0qon17.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567217\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xifhh8yj20zk0qon17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xifhh8yj20zk0qon17.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xifhh8yj20zk0qon17-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj6ml25j20qo0zkq8l.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567219\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj6ml25j20qo0zkq8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj6ml25j20qo0zkq8l.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj6ml25j20qo0zkq8l-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj94wxwj21be0qojxp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567220\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj94wxwj21be0qojxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj94wxwj21be0qojxp.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xj94wxwj21be0qojxp-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjdxa2zj20qo0zkwht.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567221\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjdxa2zj20qo0zkwht.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjdxa2zj20qo0zkwht.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjdxa2zj20qo0zkwht-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjf4a4vj20k00zkdhm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567222\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjf4a4vj20k00zkdhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjf4a4vj20k00zkdhm.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjf4a4vj20k00zkdhm-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/67218d03ly1fj4xjf4a4vj20k00zkdhm-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2050324371/FjUplweI6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@梁予庆律师</a>：开学伊始，孙女的老师发圣旨要求学生和家长收看央视一套的《开学第一课》，并上传照片到班级群相册去，年轻人有事外出，只有我这老爷子陪孙女上课了，不期却遇上董卿主持，听着她娓娓讲述汉字的故事，倒让我这个傍听生到入迷了！ ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/7a357793gy1fj4wtqc3psj20qo1bfwkx.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-567212\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/7a357793gy1fj4wtqc3psj20qo1bfwkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/7a357793gy1fj4wtqc3psj20qo1bfwkx.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/7a357793gy1fj4wtqc3psj20qo1bfwkx-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_567213\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/IMG_1624.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-567213\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/IMG_1624.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"835\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/IMG_1624.jpg 649w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/IMG_1624-162x300.jpg 162w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/IMG_1624-552x1024.jpg 552w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博图片</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p>@杭之冯玥均建国后成精：开学第一课绝对是中国收视率最高的电视节目之一。 ​​​​</p>\n<p>科华路潇洒哥：第一次把电视节目放进了家庭作业里面</p>\n<p>@橘子81哭：看，还得拍照。</p>\n<p>@小孟湖61：前几次我都是让娃拿ipad摆拍（没电视机），然后我第二天拖快进看一点拼写观后感交差，今年老师让娃自己写了，要求300字，明天得看点回放。</p>\n<p>@高等游民X：毕竟教委规定的任务，必须看还得拍照为证，每年都一样，个人比较反感</p>\n<p>@共君一醉：老婆是老师，说学校要求的学生都要看</p>\n<p>@aoe518：所有中小学校都要求学生看，还得写观后感</p>\n<p>@Lesliessssi：原来全中国的老师都布置了这个作业[费解]陪我弟弟看了一下简直～一带一路 文化输出？？</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,10466,27949],"tags":[10755,25917,31267,15552,9375,20162,33415]}